MOTION DOCKET

99-239. State v. Reiner.

Lucas App. No. L-97-1002. On motion for procedural clarification following remand from Supreme Court of the United States and motion to set briefing schedule and oral argument. Motion to set briefing schedule granted and motion for oral argument denied.

Cook, J., would deny both the motion to set briefing schedule and the motion for oral argument. Resnick, J., not participating.
